      "id": "PopularPost245785",
      "post_content": "I rate this card well because Magic is not always about brute effectiveness. Sometimes it's about flavor and art, and this is a classic in that regard. In modern times (if banding was still being printed) it would probably cost 2 colorless less, and at that price it would shut down some red decks. As-is, I still think of it fondly and use it in the occasional casual deck.",
